North America


























Investec Securities (US) LLC is a Financial Industry Regulatory Authority, Inc. (FINRA) specialist broker-dealer focusing on equities of the United Kingdom, South Africa, Ireland, Hong Kong and India.
Research Distribution
Investec Group possesses research teams in the United Kingdom, South Africa, Ireland and Hong Kong. Investec Securities distributes third-party affiliate research to its client base in the United States and Canada. For more information about Investec’s United Kingdom, South African, Irish, Hong Kong and Indian research products, please see the links below:

UK - Investec Bank plc
SA - Investec Securities Limited
IR - Investec Bank plc
HK - Investec Capital Asia Limited
IN - Investec Capital Services (India) Private Limited


Corporate Access
Investec Securities brings analysts, corporate officers and policy makers to its institutional client base to discuss the markets, corporate progress and political considerations affecting investments.
Intermediation
Investec Securities intermediates securities transactions for major US institutional investors pursuant to US Securities and Exchange Commission Rule 15a-6.


























